Mizuki: <Night, everyone!>
Mizuki: Mhm... Man, I slept great...!
Mizuki: But I still feel really drowsy. I guess I did stay up pretty late last night.
Mizuki: Oh, it's 10:00...? I don't have school or work today, so I can go back to... Wait!
Mizuki: Our new song! What are people saying about it?
Mizuki: Huh?! It has this many views already?! In less than half a day...?
Comment: <N25's new song's amazing!>
Comment: <I didn't know they could make music like this.>
Comment: <I've had a lot on my mind lately, but I feel way better after hearing this song.>
Mizuki: (Thank goodness... It's reaching everyone.)
Mizuki: (The others really put everything they had into this song, so I couldn't be happier.)
Mizuki: (Especially Kanade... She really is an incredible person...)
Mizuki: (It all started with Mafuyu saying, “This isn't good enough.” And now, she's found a way to reach not just Mafuyu, but all these other people...)
Mizuki: (It's not just Kanade either. Mafuyu and Ena are also really amazing people.)
Mizuki: (They're taking a hard look at themselves and facing their problems despite how uncomfortable that might be.)
Mizuki: (But look at me...)
Mizuki: (I haven't changed at all.)
Mizuki: (I'm still stuck in the same place...)
Mizuki: Huh? A message? At this time?
