Mizuki: (An after party...)
Mizuki: (I want to go, but...)
Ena: <You're coming, right?>
Ena: <These things aren't as fun when you're not there.>
Mizuki: Ena...
Mizuki: <Yeah, I'll be there.>
Mizuki: <Poor, lonely Ena♪>
Mizuki: Haha... Yup, she's mad.
Mizuki: But Ena really is a good person... I mean, she's willing to put up with me like this.
